[SDG-MANGO-HELPERS]: Use dmsbars to toggle individual bars or apply full presets (classic, windows-like, mac-like, combo, sidebar, side+status)
[SDG-MANGO-HELPERS]: Switch between layouts instantly with manlayout — scroller, tile, grid, deck, fair, monocle, and dwindle
[SDG-MANGO-HELPERS]: Use mangoconf to browse and edit your mangoWM config files with fzf and bat previews
[SDG-MANGO-HELPERS]: Use manmenu to see a description of any config line — press Alt+b to open the relevant docs
[SDG-MANGO-HELPERS]: Mark a workspace, move to another, and run swapmarked to exchange all windows between them
[SDG-MANGO-HELPERS]: The RGB daemon syncs your keyboard lighting to keymode and theme changes automatically
[SDG-MANGO-HELPERS]: layoutbutton shows the current layout in your bar and runs per-layout side effects (zoom, group-all, etc.)
